description_zh: 鼓励原创的技术创作，提供可信赖的内容，挖掘技术的价值，培育分享的土壤。
description_en: Encourage original technical creations, provide reliable content, explore the value of technology, and cultivate a fertile ground for sharing.
rating_zh: 可以分享自己的产品，但直接写推广文效果可能比较差。
rating_en: You can share your own products, but directly writing promotional texts may not yield good results.
